---
import Analytics from "@vercel/analytics/astro";

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Charizard Token ($CHZ) Litepaper outlining the vision, tokenomics, mechanics, and roadmap of this deflationary crypto asset."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/assets/logo.png" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/logo.png" />
    <title>Charizard Token Litepaper | $CHZ</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg-main: #050309;
        --bg-secondary: rgba(26, 12, 40, 0.7);
        --brand-fire: #ff7930;
        --brand-dragon: #ff4c20;
        --brand-ember: #ffd166;
        --text-primary: #f7f7ff;
        --text-muted: rgba(247, 247, 255, 0.78);
        --divider: rgba(255, 138, 71, 0.32);
        font-family: "Segoe UI", "Inter", "Roboto", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255, 98, 0, 0.16), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(118, 45, 158, 0.18), transparent 60%), var(--bg-main);
        color: var(--text-primary);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        min-height: 100vh;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      header {
        padding: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem) clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
        max-width: 1040px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        width: min(280px, 70vw);
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto 1.6rem;
        display: block;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 1.4rem rgba(255, 120, 40, 0.35));
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      header p {
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 720px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      main {
        flex: 1;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1040px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.4rem) clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 3rem) 4rem;
        display: grid;
        gap: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      }

      section {
        background: var(--bg-secondary);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 138, 71, 0.22);
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
        box-shadow: 0 1.2rem 2.8rem rgba(6, 0, 11, 0.4);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      }

      section h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      section h3 {
        margin-top: 1.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--brand-ember);
      }

      p,
      li {
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      ul,
      ol {
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        margin: 0.8rem 0 0;
      }

      .stat-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: 1.3rem;
      }

      .stat {
        background: rgba(18, 8, 28, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 111, 48, 0.28);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
      }

      .stat span {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.82);
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      }

      .stat strong {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
      }

      blockquote {
        margin: 1.4rem 0;
        padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-fire);
        background: rgba(18, 7, 28, 0.7);
        border-radius: 12px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        header {
          padding: 2.3rem 1.2rem;
        }

        main {
          padding: 1.6rem 1rem 3rem;
        }

        section {
          padding: 1.5rem 1.3rem;
        }

        .stat-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <img
        src="/assets/logo.png"
        alt="Charizard Token emblem"
        class="logo"
        width="360"
        height="360"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <h1>Charizard Token Litepaper</h1>
      <p>
        $CHZ is a deflationary, community-driven asset inspired by Charizard’s relentless flame. This litepaper details the mission, mechanics,
        and execution strategy that fuel our push to ignite wealth for every holder.
      </p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section>
        <h2>Vision &amp; Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Charizard Token seeks to channel the energy of the legendary fire dragon into a crypto ecosystem that rewards conviction, speed, and
          community coordination. Our mission is to create a hyper-engaged economy where scarcity is engineered, growth is community-led, and the
          upside belongs to those who help the flame grow.
        </p>
        <blockquote>
          Empower early believers, weaponize burns for scarcity, and transform holders into the next generation of crypto millionaires.
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Token Fundamentals</h2>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Total Supply</span>
            <strong>1,000,000,000 $CHZ</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Ticker</span>
            <strong>$CHZ</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Network</span>
            <strong>Solana</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Deflation</span>
            <strong>Dynamic Burns</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3>Allocation Philosophy</h3>
        <p>
          Supply is intentionally concentrated toward liquidity depth and community expansion. Team and treasury allocations are time-locked, ensuring
          long-term alignment. Burn reserves are reserved for milestone celebrations that simultaneously reward holders and harden scarcity.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Buy &amp; Entry Mechanics</h2>
        <p>
          Acquisition is streamlined to minimize friction for newcomers. Current OTC entry terms prioritize fair launch principles and immediate
          liquidity support.
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Transfer SOL to the treasury address <strong>9Vsan6w7QaGHDEbF1JcgruDVcbsS3xkEMgeZmAQGJ5wP</strong></li>
          <li>Receive $CHZ at the live OTC rate — presently 0.1 SOL equals 350,000 $CHZ.</li>
          <li>Holder addresses are recorded for airdrop eligibility and governance onboarding.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Deflationary Engine</h2>
        <p>
          Burns are integral to Charizard Token. We deploy multi-layered scarcity mechanics that tighten circulating supply while rewarding active
          participants.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Auto Burns:</strong> A percentage of ecosystem fees feeds into a rolling burn queue executed weekly.</li>
          <li><strong>Event Burns:</strong> Major milestones trigger ceremonial burns that celebrate community achievements.</li>
          <li><strong>Quest Burns:</strong> Gamified campaigns let holders vote on targets, choosing what gets incinerated next.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Every burn is transparently documented, reinforcing trust and showcasing the flame’s intensity to the broader crypto audience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Utility Stack</h2>
        <p>
          $CHZ is designed for speed and engagement. Low-cost Solana transactions enable rapid movement, while utility layers keep holders plugged into
          the fire.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Staking &amp; Embers:</strong> Lock $CHZ to earn ember rewards that scale during burn events.</li>
          <li><strong>Lore-Driven NFTs:</strong> Collect Charizard-themed assets that grant Discord upgrades, merch drops, and metaverse arena access.</li>
          <li><strong>GameFi Integrations:</strong> Battle in cross-protocol quests where performance determines burn votes and reward pools.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Roadmap Execution</h2>
        <p>
          Our roadmap follows the Charizard evolutionary arc, with each phase expanding capabilities while accelerating deflation.
        </p>
        <h3>Phase 01 // Spark</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Launch $CHZ with fortified liquidity pools and transparent contracts.</li>
          <li>Distribute genesis airdrop to validated flame-bearers.</li>
          <li>Execute first ceremonial burn to establish the scarcity baseline.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Phase 02 // Blaze</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Secure cross-exchange listings and bootstrap arbitrage incentives.</li>
          <li>Release lore-driven NFT collections and integrate with partner GameFi titles.</li>
          <li>Enable cross-chain bridges to invite new battlegrounds.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Phase 03 // Inferno</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Transition to DAO-led governance with ember-weighted voting.</li>
          <li>Run recurring deflation events coordinated by the community council.</li>
          <li>Launch global raids, IRL activations, and branded experiences.
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Community &amp; Governance</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in firepower through participation. Holders shape the ecosystem, elect multisig guardians, and steer the burn cadence via on-chain
          voting. Transparent treasury dashboards and weekly war-room calls keep every dragon rider informed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Risk &amp; Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Charizard Token is a high-volatility digital asset. Market swings, regulatory shifts, and smart contract vulnerabilities can impact value.
          Participants should conduct independent research and only deploy capital they are prepared to risk. Team allocations are locked, but no
          outcome is guaranteed.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © {year} Charizard Token. Fan-made homage inspired by Charizard. Always do your own research.
    </footer>

    <Analytics />
  </body>
</html>
